@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000/api

### Health
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Upload files
POST {{baseUrl}}/imports/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="resume_dataset.csv"
Content-Type: text/csv

< ../resume_dataset.csv
--boundary--

### Files
GET {{baseUrl}}/imports/files

### Candidates
GET {{baseUrl}}/candidates?page=1&page_size=25

### Dashboard stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/stats

### Generate dashboard charts
POST {{baseUrl}}/dashboard/generate

